<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Contrat sponsor - {{ sponsor.companyName ?: 'EventFlow' }}</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: DejaVu Sans, Arial, sans-serif;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #1f2937;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background: #ffffff;
        }

        .page {
            padding: 28px 26px 22px;
        }

        .head {
            display: table;
            width: 100%;
            margin-bottom: 18px;
            border-bottom: 2px solid #e5e7eb;
            padding-bottom: 12px;
        }

        .head-left,
        .head-right {
            display: table-cell;
            vertical-align: middle;
        }

        .head-right {
            text-align: right;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: flex-end;
            justify-content: center;
        }

        .sponsor-brand {
            width: 96px;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 6px;
        }

        .sponsor-logo-wrap {
            width: 84px;
            height: 84px;
            border-radius: 12px;
            border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
            background: #f9fafb;
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            overflow: hidden;
            margin-bottom: 0;
        }

        .sponsor-logo {
            max-width: 100%;
            max-height: 100%;
            object-fit: contain;
        }

        .sponsor-logo-fallback {
            font-size: 26px;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #6b7280;
        }

        .brand-logo {
            height: 42px;
            margin-bottom: 6px;
        }

        .title {
            font-size: 22px;
            font-weight: 700;
            margin: 0;
            color: #111827;
        }

        .subtitle {
            font-size: 12px;
            margin: 4px 0 0;
            color: #6b7280;
        }

        .company {
            font-size: 16px;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #111827;
            line-height: 1.2;
            text-align: center;
            width: 100%;
            word-break: break-word;
        }

        .meta {
            margin: 16px 0;
            border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 10px 12px;
            background: #f9fafb;
        }

        .meta p {
            margin: 4px 0;
            font-size: 12px;
        }

        .section {
            margin-top: 16px;
            border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 12px 14px;
        }

        .section h2 {
            margin: 0 0 10px;
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #111827;
        }

        .list {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            list-style: none;
        }

        .list li {
            margin-bottom: 7px;
        }

        .paragraph {
            line-height: 1.55;
            margin: 0 0 8px;
            color: #374151;
        }

        .signatures {
            margin-top: 26px;
            display: table;
            width: 100%;
        }

        .sign-box {
            display: table-cell;
            width: 50%;
            vertical-align: bottom;
            padding-right: 16px;
        }

        .sign-box:last-child {
            padding-right: 0;
            padding-left: 16px;
        }

        .sign-label {
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #374151;
            margin-bottom: 28px;
            display: block;
        }

        .sign-line {
            border-bottom: 1px solid #111827;
            height: 1px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="page">
        <header class="head">
            <div class="head-left">
                <img class="brand-logo" src="{{ absolute_url(asset('images/logo.png')) }}" alt="EventFlow">
                <h1 class="title">Contrat Sponsor</h1>
                <p class="subtitle">Document de partenariat EventFlow</p>
            </div>
            <div class="head-right">
                <div class="sponsor-brand">
                    <div class="sponsor-logo-wrap">
                        {% if sponsor.logoUrl %}
                            <img class="sponsor-logo" src="{{ sponsor.logoUrl }}" alt="{{ sponsor.companyName ?: 'Logo sponsor' }}">
                        {% else %}
                            <span class="sponsor-logo-fallback">{{ (sponsor.companyName ?: 'SP')|slice(0, 2)|upper }}</span>
                        {% endif %}
                    </div>
                    <div class="company">{{ sponsor.companyName ?: 'Sponsor' }}</div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </header>

        <section class="meta">
            <p><strong>Date:</strong> {{ generatedAt|date('d/m/Y') }}</p>
            <p><strong>Evenement:</strong> {{ eventTitle }}</p>
            {% if event and event.location %}
                <p><strong>Lieu:</strong> {{ event.location }}</p>
            {% endif %}
            {% if event and event.startDate %}
                <p><strong>Debut:</strong> {{ event.startDate|date('d/m/Y H:i') }}</p>
            {% endif %}
        </section>

        <section class="section">
            <h2>Informations Sponsor</h2>
            <ul class="list">
                <li><strong>Entreprise:</strong> {{ sponsor.companyName ?: '-' }}</li>
                <li><strong>Email:</strong> {{ sponsor.contactEmail ?: '-' }}</li>
                <li><strong>Contribution:</strong> {{ sponsor.contributionAmount|number_format(2, ',', ' ') }} DT</li>
                <li><strong>Numero fiscal:</strong> {{ sponsor.taxId ?: '-' }}</li>
                <li><strong>Secteur:</strong> {{ sponsor.industry ?: '-' }}</li>
                <li><strong>Telephone:</strong> {{ sponsor.phone ?: '-' }}</li>
            </ul>
        </section>

        <section class="section">
            <h2>Engagement</h2>
            <p class="paragraph">Le sponsor confirme sa contribution a l'evenement mentionne ci-dessus.</p>
            <p class="paragraph">La contribution est affectee aux besoins organisationnels, a la communication et aux ressources liees a l'evenement.</p>
            <p class="paragraph">Ce document formalise l'accord de sponsoring entre EventFlow et l'entreprise sponsor.</p>
        </section>

        <section class="signatures">
            <div class="sign-box">
                <span class="sign-label">Signature Organisateur</span>
                <div class="sign-line"></div>
            </div>
            <div class="sign-box">
                <span class="sign-label">Signature Sponsor</span>
                <div class="sign-line"></div>
            </div>
        </section>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
